This folder contains information how to install
Coin3D to be used as ROOT OpenGL viewer

1. Download: http://www.coin3d.org/Coin/about.php
    The source code is available from 
    http://www.coin3d.org/Coin/dl_src.php

    One has to download and install 4 different things:

    1. Coin3D
    2. SmallChange
    3. SoQt
    4. simage
    5. SoGuiExamples 

    See: checkOut.sh script.

2. Install http://www.coin3d.org/Coin/building.php 
   Under Windows one MUST not install Coin into the default directory 
   because Fons skips ones.

   See: installCoin3D.sh
